features.name: GTP_EFTU,GTP_EFTU_D2,RF3_C Increases the formation of ribosomal termination complexes and stimulates activities of RF-1 and RF-2. The stimulation of RF- 1 and RF-2 is significantly reduced by GTP and GDP, but not by GMP
